<lb n="0139b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0139b0901" type="dharani">唵醯伊吽吽娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0139b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0139b1001">十八毘樓博叉密語。</p>
<lb n="0139b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0139b1101" type="dharani">唵摩兜祇浦屈沙底娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0139b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0139b1201">十九毘沙門天密語。</p>
<lb n="0139b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0139b1301" type="dharani">唵南無帝南跋折羅祇叉婆羅弭他南<note n="0139015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南＋（無）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0139015" resp="【原】" corr="南無">南</sic>壁
<lb n="0139b14" ed="T"/>室良半拏耶婆<note n="0139016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">良＋（叉）【甲】</note><app n="0139016"><lem wit="【大】">良</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">良叉</rdg></app>耶娑婆訶</p>
